	(text "Flumper is a high speed (480Mbps) dual channel programmer board supporting \nJTAG, SPI, I2C and UART for targets at 1.8V, 2.5V, 3.3V and 5V using level shifting. \nPhysical isolation between the programmer board and target can be controlled over USB."
