	(text "The external EEPROM can also be used to customise the USB VID, PID, Serial Number, Product\nDescription Strings and Power Descriptor value of the FT2232H for OEM applications. Other parameters\ncontrolled by the EEPROM include Remote Wake Up, Soft Pull Down on Power-Off and I/O pin drive\nstrength.\nIf the FT2232H is used without an external EEPROM the chip defaults to a USB to FT232 asynchronous\nserial interface port device. If no EEPROM is connected (or the EEPROM is blank), the FT2232H uses its\nbuilt-in default VID (0403), PID (6010) Product Description and Power Descriptor Value. In this case, the\ndevice will not have a serial number as part of the USB descriptor."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 47.752 96.52 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1 1)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "ff65a27c-6a85-4eaa-b6f4-678a56b7a0bb")
	)
